external_knowledge:
A seasoned player refers to one who has played more than 10 games; 
Average win rate is the mean of win rates; 
Highest kills is the maximum number of kills achieved in a single game; 
Minimum total minutes played is the least total time spent playing; 
Total matches won against AI refers to the sum of matches won against artificial intelligence opponents.

sql:
SELECT player_id, total_games, wins
FROM player_stats
ORDER BY total_games DESC;
